<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd">
<html>

<head>
    <title>Processing Template</title>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/p5.js/0.4.13/p5.js"></script>
    <script>
    var circleX = 0;
        var circleY = 100;
        var circleL = 500;
        var circleW = 50;
        var circleK = 100;
        var circleO=50;
        var circleJ=100;
        var circleH = 100;
        var circleStroke = 0;
        var circleFill = 0;
        var backgroundColor = 255;
        var change = 0.25;

        function setup() {
            createCanvas(500,500);
            background(random(255),random(255),random(255));
           
            
            centerX =100 
            centerY= height/2 ; 
            scale = 1; 
            frameRate (100);
            opacity = 225;
         var x = 0;

         while(x <= 600){
               line(x,0,x,600);
               x = x + 10;



         var y=0;
         while (y <= 600){
             line(0,y,600,y);
             y += 10;
         }
         }
        }


        function draw() {
            fill(random(255),random(255),random(255));
            stroke(circleStroke);
            ellipse(circleX, circleY, circleW, circleH);
            ellipse(circleL, circleK, circleO, circleJ);

            circleX += change;
            circleY += change;
            circleL -= change;
            circleK += change;
            
         
         
         


        }

        function mouseDragged(){

          stroke(random(255),random(255),random(255));
         line(mouseX,mouseY,0,0);                   
         line(500,500,mouseX,mouseY);
         line(500,0,mouseX,mouseY);
         line(0,500,mouseX,mouseY);
          line(10,690,mouseX,mouseY);
           line(500,70,mouseX,mouseY);
            line(130,700,mouseX,mouseY);
           line(800,40,mouseX,mouseY);
            line(170,780,mouseX,mouseY);
           line(800,90,mouseX,mouseY);


         fill(mouseX,0,mouseY,0);
         ellipse(mouseX,mouseY,255,255);
         ellipse(mouseX,mouseY,150,00);
         fill(mouseX,900,mouseY,900);
         ellipse(mouseX,mouseY,50,10);
         ellipse(mouseX,mouseY,30,60);

        }
      
             
             
                function keyPressed(){
             
          
             



}

        
    </script>
</head>
